author: LegoBatmanLandon
title: It's a key chain. What do you expect?
review:
this is a somewhat good value for the price of $5, but key chains are minifigures or builds that are glued together, unless you have a pair of pliers or a lighter, the min ifig will remain 1 piece.

 

Pros: looks good when hung on a backpack, it's Darth Vader!!!!!!!

Cons: remains 1 piece.
